OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA generally
OL,6,Fmild night with cloud thickening from
OL,7,Fthe west into the evening, bringing a
OL,8,Ffew showers or outbreaks of rain,
OL,9,Fmainly affecting western and northern
OL,10,Fareas by dawn on Friday morning. Winds
OL,11,Fremaining light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FCloudier on Friday, but
OL,14,Fprobably drier conditions developing
OL,15,Fduring the morning. However more rain
OL,16,Farriving from the south Friday
OL,17,Fafternoon, perhaps turning heavier and
OL,18,Fmore persistent. Feeling colder than
OL,19,Frecently.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
